  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/679390/extras/389a002cb2da2ffffc467c93b6cfe20b.avif?t=1644433840\" width=500 height=134 /></span></h2><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/679390/extras/b4fb0c57bab30107cbd7ea046aec3abe.webp?t=1644433840\" width=118 height=27 /></span><br><br>Topdown Showdown is a smash inspired fighting game with a top down perspective. Dodge, combo, and knock your opponents out of the arena, from any angle!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/679390/extras/fe3ceeb7350b8ddc735a64efebc82b9d.webp?t=1644433840\" width=108 height=27 /></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Choose from a roster of 17 characters in local or online versus 1v1 play.<br></li><li> Fast, aggressive game-play style designed to promote diverse and skillful combos hidden beneath a simple control scheme<br></li><li> Rollback netcode</li></ul>",
